    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium leather upholstery is supple and clean, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronics, from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, having followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule with recent fluid changes and a fresh set of high-performance tires. It drives straight and true, offering a smooth, quiet ride that reflects its pampered history. This is an ideal choice for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-end experience without the new-car price tag.",
